window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the aftermath of the demonic invasion, everyone is left to recover. Claire is worried about Doc's unending sleep. Fiora and her adventurers have split up, and the royal family mourns the loss of the prince and princess. </p> <p>Meanwhile, people are baying for blood as news spreads, and the church comes in to eliminate any demonic forces remaining. Tensions rise as the clergy begins its own agenda with the dungeon. Through it all, a town comes together with a unique bond to Doc. </p> <p>The uneasy peace won't last long, however, because in this world of adventure, trouble comes in all shapes and sizes. </p>"; 
